br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，我只係用新香港邏輯諗嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"如果賣去美國，香港產都要寫中國產"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:19:16.000Z","msg":"外銷等級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ece067b1049c5725983f06bbe11f6cd6cecd97","tid":2349981,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"唔係咁撚爆呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c35999953bb1ff1f3ee861ae977178d76d8682b","tid":2349981,"uid":165136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"packing 嗰時喺中國，當時係本地<br />\n之後運到香港無改原裝lable 啫"},{"pid":"c63f9560a24b1ac6aaa69e3d4d312d106b8eb2f8","tid":2349981,"uid":167007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"中國未本地<br />\n你係未想分裂中國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51aac02b3b7528cef3ff996737b1765fd74c211","tid":2349981,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"457a452a1ed1385d8c890d92312c047f83cd0e1f","tid":2349981,"uid":58630,"like":405,"dislike":1,"score":404,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"有機本地 即係有可能係亦都可以係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4099952c4deb7366bddf8cd20e9edb197c72f9","tid":2349981,"uid":16518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7162aaf416fe604180b327f4330caed590088458","tid":2349981,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"457a452a1ed1385d8c890d92312c047f83cd0e1f","tid":2349981,"uid":58630,"like":405,"dislike":1,"score":404,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"有機本地 即係有可能係亦都可以係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmo